channel.title: Need help with my rsps please!
channel.description: Hello guys, Ive had my server up for like a week but yesterday i had this issue where i couldent login to my server because i got error connecting to server when i clicked login but im not sure why..Because other people was on and others could get on.Its just me and im not sure why i cant get on to my own server.Please help guys i can either pay 1m rsgp or owner on my server if you help im really struggled by this.Thanks community of moparscape!

item.title: Need help with my rsps please!
item.dc:creator: @grimpkz1 grimpkz1
item.description:
@grimpkz1 wrote:

Go to your client.java and change the ip of the server to “127.0.0.1”. I suggest you do ctrl + f and find “server =”, just change them to 127.0.0.1

Make sure the one you’re changing doesn’t have any of these next to it. “//” because it wouldn’t work.
